This isn=E2=80=99t that big of a surprise: the number of new shows was goin=
g to go down regardless, given the unsustainable nature of streaming spendi=
ng over the last several years. What is notable is that Hollywood studios a=
ren=E2=80=99t waiting to start cutting; from Matthew Belloni at Puck ( http=
s://puck.news/and-now-the-tv-purge-begins/ ) :

